# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This is a DOCS-ONLY repository. Never commit source, data, or
# secrets here. The patterns below are a safety net against
# accidental copies of the application into this repo.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Secrets / credentials
.env
.env.*
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets*
credentials*

# Application source & runtime (do NOT publish)
src/
public/
tools/
scripts/
node_modules/
package-lock.json

# User & trading data (do NOT publish)
data/
*.db
*.sqlite

# Server / infra
nginx*
*.conf
dump.pm2
*.log

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
